OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBrisk winds
OL,6,Fand showers will ease overnight, and
OL,7,Fit will become mostly dry by morning.
OL,8,FSome clear spells developing under
OL,9,Flighter winds, allowing for a chilly
OL,10,Fend to the night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FThe odd early shower is
OL,13,Fpossible, otherwise a dry day with
OL,14,Flight winds. Cloudy at times, but with
OL,15,Fsome bright or sunny spells. Feeling
OL,16,Fless chilly in lighter winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
